snippet.title: Burnout Paradise - Guns N' Roses Trailer
snippet.description: Take me down to Paradise City!  Guns N' Roses tears up the road with the ultimate rock anthem that symbolizes the ultimate in rebellious behavior and gets your adrenaline pumping.  Burnout Paradise offers a truly volatile mix of rock's most dangerous tracks -- beginning with the iconic 'Paradise City' -- for an audio fuel as explosive as the game itself.  Seeing how Burnout is one of the world's most popular racing franchises, it demands a soundtrack that matches the game's intensity at every level.
